         <abstract>
            <p>This paper outlines the conception and development of rating brakes. It is related to the adoption of the snub method of rating brakes as described in SAE Recommended Practice J880 and proposes an alternate continuous drag test method utilizing a dynamometer adapted to a road vehicle.</p>
